OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy as bands of
OL,6,Frain push northeast in the morning.
OL,7,FRain will turn showery later, these
OL,8,Fshowers heavy and thundery at times.
OL,9,FWindy at times, especially around the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear spells and scattered
OL,13,Fshowers through the evening and
OL,14,Fovernight, these showers will be heavy
OL,15,Fat times. Windy around the coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,18,Fscattered showers. Becoming mostly dry
OL,19,Fby the evening as showers fade out.
OL,20,FBreezy around the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
